 datasets, and was tested in both healthy and Parkinson's\nDisease (PD) gait. Results demonstrate the extracted muscle activity levels in\na healthy subject's level ground walking, and the extracted HS events of a PD\npatient. Adjustments to algorithm parameters are possible (e.g., expected\nvelocity, cadence) and can further increase the detection accuracy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Feb 2023 18:19:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-09"}
