m-1, with the best result\nof 9.9cm-1 with B97-1/def2-TZVPD. Appropriate matching of double-zeta basis\nsets with hybrid functionals can produce high quality results. The B97-1,\nTPSS0-D3(BJ) or wB97X-D hybrid functionals with 6-31G*, pc-1 or pcseg-1 are\nrecommended for fast routine calculations, all delivering median errors of\n11-12cm-1.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Feb 2023 05:46:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-10"}
