 the assigned path.\nAlong with several simulated experiments, we present a real-world experiment in\na natural forest, showcasing the validity and effectiveness of the proposed\ncollective navigation approach in challenging environments. The source code is\nreleased as open-source, making it possible to replicate the obtained results\nand facilitate the continuation of research by the community.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Feb 2023 15:32:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-13"}
